{"tid":2205275,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蘭州生物藥廠洩漏布魯氏菌事故　財新揭陽性感染者破數千　較官方原先公布高十多倍","createTime":"2020-09-16T16:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T18:22:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff0b767a4f2eca235f54d7f56a40c3ef2239bc7d","tid":2205275,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:40:50.000Z","msg":"蘭州生物藥廠去年7、8月期間生產獸用布魯氏菌疫苗時發生洩漏，含布魯氏菌的氣溶膠隨排放的廢氣散播到附近地區。<br />\n<br />\n官方去年底公布的調查結果，指事件中一共有203人感染。包括藥廠附近的蘭州獸研所和蘭州大學的師生，除了一人有臨床症狀，其餘都無症狀、無發病。當局又指定11間醫院為附近居民免費檢測，但無再公布感染人數。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，真正的感染數字是官方公布的十多倍。內地《財新網》日前報道截至今年2月底，有2萬名蘭州市民進行了檢測，約5000人在初步篩查後布魯氏菌抗體呈陽性，確認陽性感染者超過3000人。其中位於藥廠附近的鹽場堡社區，就有至少有2500名居民被感染。<br />\n<br />\n《財新網》訪問了部分患者，化名杜偉的居民去年底脊柱發痛和發燒後主動和太太進行檢測，兩人的滴度是1比400 。按國家標準，滴度1比100以上就是確診，但醫生卻強調他們有抗體好像免費打了疫苗，又指3至6個月內體內病菌會自然減少，不危害健康。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/35595\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F35595&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2Bu6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=e65dcda6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F35595&h=e69c91e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/35595</a>"},{"pid":"f550a365ad14eb5e73d06ddb6ab101501a9dd823","tid":2205275,"uid":50745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:42:12.000Z","msg":"有害病菌不危害健康。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9497dc8803a774fe0494a41feef8bc10b5474bf","tid":2205275,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f550a365ad14eb5e73d06ddb6ab101501a9dd823","tid":2205275,"uid":50745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:42:12.000Z","msg":"有害病菌不危害健康。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:43:00.000Z","msg":"有抗體好像免費打了疫苗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3f755e18b409e106c784f0736f53e707a5e5ef","tid":2205275,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T18:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}